    feat: Complete ChatGPT-like UI with comprehensive improvements
    
     Major Features:
    - Full ChatGPT-like interface with multi-chat system (max 3 concurrent chats)
    - Document upload and URL processing directly in chat interface
    - Real-time typing indicators with smooth animations
    - Message timestamps and date headers for better context
    - Dark/light mode toggle with fluid animations
    - Comprehensive error handling with toast notifications
    
     UI/UX Improvements:
    - User and bot icons for message identification
    - Dynamic input field with auto-resize and proper scrollbar handling
    - Send button positioning and hover state fixes
    - Responsive sidebar with chat history
    - Modern rounded corners and smooth transitions
    - Proper color contrast for all text elements
    
     Technical Fixes:
    - Fixed LLM response formatting (markdown, HTML, line breaks)
    - Resolved incomplete code block rendering (blue bar issue)
    - Converted backtick-wrapped URLs to clickable links
    - Implemented model pre-loading to prevent JIT loading
    - Added request queuing to prevent concurrent interference
    - Disabled embeddings to use text-based similarity
    - Enhanced URL fetching with Cloudflare challenge handling
    
     Error Handling & Stability:
    - Comprehensive error boundaries and toast notifications
    - Graceful fallbacks for failed operations
    - Server-side document cleanup on chat deletion
    - Robust API error handling with user-friendly messages
    - Fixed undici compatibility issues by removing cheerio
    
     Performance Optimizations:
    - Sequential document processing to prevent model conflicts
    - Model loading state management
    - Efficient message rendering with proper cleanup
    - Optimized CSS with custom variables for theming
    
     Configuration:
    - Updated environment variables for LM Studio integration
    - Model name standardization across all components
    - Disabled embeddings for simplified operation
    - Enhanced webpack configuration for compatibility

